}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== Per the FCC block diagram, this device has 4MB Flash and 16MB RAM.
"613A200049 0336" is silkscreened on the wireless module in the FCC photos. A MAC label affixed to the module has an 00:03:C9 ('''[[Tecom]]''') OUI.
